The complete assembly language source code for all of the utilities on the
Utility Disk #1.   Well commented and modularized, many other programs
can be written that take advantage of these routines.  The code has been
written for use with the Tandy ALDS assembler.  The code purposely avoids
macros and other assembler-specific operations, so converting it for use
with your favorite assembler should be easy.

